com.ucsf.core.data

Class SharedTables.GroundTrust

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ucsf.core.data.SharedTables.GroundTrust
  • Enclosing class:
    SharedTables

    public abstract static class SharedTables.GroundTrust
extends java.lang.Object
    Table storing ground trust data, i.e. a data category, a label and time range. Fields are:
    - DataManager.KEY_PATIENT_ID [TEXT] : Unique id of the patient
    - DataManager.KEY_IS_COMMITTED [BOOLEAN]: Indicates if the entry has been synchronized with a remote device
    - KEY_TYPE [TEXT] : Type of data we want to label
    - KEY_LABEL [TEXT] : Label of the data
    - KEY_START [TEXT] : Timestamp corresponding to the start of the acquisition.
    - KEY_END [TEXT] : Timestamp corresponding to the end of the acquisition.
